This paper proposes a CPU-GPU heterogenous implementation for the Winograd algorithm.

Recommended citation: Senhao Shao, Yizhuo Wang, Weixing Ji, Jianhua Gao. (2022). &quot;Towards Optimal Fast Matrix Multiplication on CPU-GPU Platforms.&quot; <i>International Conference on Parallel and Distributed Computing: Applications and Technologies (PDCAT)</i>. 223–236.